        },
        {
            "title": "A股偏軟   深股表現疲弱",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股早段偏軟，深股低開後跌幅擴大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指低開18點或0.46%，報3915點，現報3928，跌5點或0.13%。    </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指低開92點或0.67%，報13633點，現報13572，跌153點或1.12</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300低開30點或0.64%，報4679點，現報4682，跌27點或0.58%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數低開31點或0.95%，報3184點，現報1522，趺3點或0.23%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15331814-a%e8%82%a1%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e8%a1%a8%e7%8f%be%e7%96%b2%e5%bc%b1",
